commit.message: Added failing pytest test as runnable example
Hides expects internals from pytest tracebacks.

Fix Python 3.7 collections ABC classes deprecation warning

Fixes #55
There is not need to check for OrderedDict without Python 2.6
Show Python warnings in CI build
Added supported versions badge in README
Travis does not support Python 3.7 yet
Remove PyPI downloads counter badge since it is not working

Merge pull request #44 from felixonmars/master

Note explicit support for Python 3.5
